title: My absolute greatest retailer ever
text:
If you are anything like me, that  read reviews before I make a purchase. I am about to make a statement and I assure you that I have not been paid or compensated in anyway whatsoever. This is my 100% statement. At first, I was a little skeptical about ordering things from Temu. Their prices were extremely low and affordable and then I assume that the quality of their merchandise was shabby. However, I have been using Temu for about a year now and my most recent purchase was $587. I must admit, that I love the quality of their products. They are very well-made and well-built I am a very loyal Temu customer. I always get exactly what I ordered and it is always less than two weeks to receive my merchandise, put on the average it takes about 7 to 10 days. If you see some thing in Temu that you like, you should definitely order it without any fear because they send you exactly what you asked for. At one point, I have ordered something, but once I received it, I decided that I really didn’t want it. I called the US based customer service and informed them that I wished to return in order. he asked me why I did not like the order, and once I gave him my reason, he informed me that he would be crediting my account immediately, which he did, and allowed me to keep the product as a gift from Temu and that is what I really call. Great customer service. On my latest order, I ordered a smart watch, and ingest a few minutes after charging it up and using it, I was blown away about how great that is, and it also having a very extremely nice,. I immediately made a phone call and text a friend with my watch and I am absolutely in love with that watch already. I’m giving you a detailed review because I want you to feel comfortable and whatever you order and if you are not satisfied, you will be credited immediately. I am an Amazon prime member, and if I had to choose between the two, Temu with win by a landslide and they also sell similar items as Amazon but for nearly half the price and believe me the products are well built. I am a Temu customer for life.
Frank S
